Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:07.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,早上醒來時  我總是被漆黑的黑灰所包圍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.36,0:00:10.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,衣服是烏黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.20,0:00:14.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,床鋪是烏黑的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.87,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,無論我觸碰了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.96,0:00:24.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,都會把它弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.88,0:00:26.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.29,0:00:28.00,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.67,0:00:29.50,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:30.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:32.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.97,0:00:36.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒…弄髒…弄髒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:45.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,弄髒弄髒弄髒弄髒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:19.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為了侍奉凱特小姐而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.16,0:02:23.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.83,0:02:26.25,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為了侍奉凱特小姐而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:32.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:38.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,雖說睡覺時會產生黑灰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.55,0:02:40.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但今早的黑灰比往常要多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,打掃起來會很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我最喜歡打掃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,會發揮作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:05.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的  比以前習慣多了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.83,0:03:06.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,確實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你差不多要被叫去打掃外面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.58,0:03:13.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,外面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對  和其他活人偶一起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.63,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,打掃整個公館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.89,0:03:26.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我要去外面…
Comment: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,---op---
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:07.78,Shadow house-title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(354,0)\blur5\pos(1519.2,1058.4)}房間的外面是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.41,0:05:12.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,第一次出去  好緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要出發了  出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:24.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我叫埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是樓上房間的米婭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:28.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請…請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.97,0:05:33.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快來  這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:34.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:39.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你有去過房間外面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:40.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣啊  外面超厲害的  一定會嚇你一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:46.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你和影大人相處得還好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們是這樣稱呼不知道名字的影家人的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:55.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我說  埃米莉可你是怎樣的人呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:05:59.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你不愛說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:01.21,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是露那種類型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:03.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來  是這邊哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.31,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,請拿點水來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.27,Shadow house-an8,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那有房梁對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:24.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,爬上那裡就能擦到天花板了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.65,0:06:26.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,在高處很開心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:37.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有好多活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為公館很大
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.17,0:06:41.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,即便有這麼多人也完全打掃不完
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.35,0:06:54.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,等你很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  可愛的新人小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是組長蘿絲瑪麗和寡言少語的露
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.65,0:07:03.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這孩子是埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:08.99,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我們四個人組成一個小組來工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:12.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我比較年長所以負責指導你們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:15.37,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過你不用太拘謹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.04,0:07:18.04,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請多關照  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:23.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼了  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.84,0:07:27.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我被嚇了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,房間的外面居然這麼廣闊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.97,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,居然有這麼多活人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:39.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我懂  不過放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:41.39,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大家都是好人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.77,0:07:45.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大多數是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過  這座公館可真是寬闊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那條通道居然是無限延伸下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.66,0:07:54.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,無限嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,才不是無限的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:02.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那條通道也是由大家打掃的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:03.75,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,由這裡所有的活人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大家能友好相處嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:12.76,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:16.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶啊  不用想多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:19.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,大家一起努力打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.14,0:08:21.43,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能為影家作貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:23.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這就是我們的幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對啊  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來  這是打掃箱和防黑灰外套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:34.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:42.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,今天只要簡單打掃就行  所以用不上防黑灰外套
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:45.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是你專用的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.17,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這些是我的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.68,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的  我們很幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:07.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,擦掉了明天又會積黑灰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:12.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,積黑灰了我們又會擦掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:16.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來吧  來工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:21.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來作貢獻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:26.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不用去想多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.67,0:09:31.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為了影家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.50,0:09:36.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來吧  來工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:40.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來作貢獻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:45.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不用去想多餘的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.06,0:09:50.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為了影家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:09:59.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:01.53,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,身上全是黑灰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.16,0:10:03.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你努力打掃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說起這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:08.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是來給我看什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.51,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,看起來像是只有腳曠工了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:40.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,除塵的房間怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.57,0:10:45.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,風勢好強  強到呼吸不了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.29,0:10:47.91,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不過已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,去外面打掃也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:53.92,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,叫米婭的活人偶教了我好多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.55,0:10:55.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:11:00.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來吧  來工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.05,0:11:05.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,來作貢獻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.60,0:11:10.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不用去想多餘的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.60,0:11:12.56,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:17.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,太好了  書和地板都沒濕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:20.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.61,0:11:22.45,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,下意識就…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:23.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,因為它剛好在我手邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:25.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:30.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,布偶被弄濕的話就無法變回原樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.46,0:11:34.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請問  要扔掉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:35.29,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就像之前那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.67,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,就放在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:43.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你對其他東西做什麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:48.93,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那個布偶可是凱特珍視的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:52.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你沒有珍視的東西所以不會懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.73,0:11:55.90,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐是我珍視的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:56.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.65,0:11:59.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特去洗澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:02.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉  凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.66,0:12:05.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我會努力打掃的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:21.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,擦不掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:25.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,汙漬擦不掉的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:32.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影家的…是…因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請凱特小姐讀給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.69,0:12:42.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你對其他東西做什麼都無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但那個布偶可是凱特珍視的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:05.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶必須要為影家作出貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:11.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,活人偶必須要為影家作出貢獻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.18,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:54.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.98,0:13:58.31,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對不起  擅自用了您的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:02.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可  你在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.78,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我試著修補了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:12.24,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是  這也是我自作主張吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.96,0:14:18.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:24.30,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我向你道歉  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒有事先跟你說不能碰  是凱特的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.64,0:14:31.80,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我氣過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:32.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.22,0:14:33.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.10,0:14:37.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這是我在晾乾玩偶時做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.81,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我會把它當做我珍視的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.69,0:14:44.23,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,它的名字是小麵包哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.73,0:14:46.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還真是喜歡麵包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.82,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,抱歉  我想問問您關於打掃的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.24,0:14:53.28,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,有一處怎麼也擦不掉的汙漬…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:06.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,它掉下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:40.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,小麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:42.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:55.11,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:03.16,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還好嗎  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:03.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:05.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,能動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:07.96,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是的  沒有損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:12.88,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,比起這個凱特小姐  非常感謝您特地出來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:16.55,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,既然這樣  我們就趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:32.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:36.32,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀  是生面孔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:38.66,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,難道你還沒有「露面」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:42.33,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,米婭  你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.00,0:17:47.54,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐  這是打掃的時候教了我很多東西的活人偶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.38,0:17:52.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這張「臉」怎麼了  怎麼會自己說話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:54.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,欸？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.01,0:17:57.72,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,貴安  凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:18:00.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,初次見面  我是薩拉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.18,0:18:07.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀凱特  你怎麼臉色這麼蒼白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.19,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,凱特小姐可是堂堂正正的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:22.03,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你還是多向薩拉的「臉」學習比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.87,0:18:24.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,失敗品小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.04,0:18:31.71,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼擅自要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.01,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,想無視薩拉的忠告嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我說啊失敗品小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:40.05,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,薩拉現在是什麼表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.35,0:18:43.14,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,您在…生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.06,0:18:46.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那麼凱特呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:49.27,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,哎呀凱特你怎麼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:51.15,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你怎麼沒有臉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.06,0:18:54.65,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我說  你現在是什麼表情呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.69,0:18:58.07,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你有在看著薩拉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.79,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,虧我還自我介紹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這樣廢物的影家人和「臉」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:12.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,遲早會被偉大的祖父大人處理掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:16.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,再見了凱特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.47,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你該慶幸今天遇到的是薩拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.47,0:19:21.26,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我不會把你們的失態告訴別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.06,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,不要用這種表情走路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.64,0:19:29.52,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影家的人要更加有自信才行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.69,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:37.73,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我是廢物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.61,0:19:41.36,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我總是在給凱特小姐添麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.41,0:19:43.57,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.58,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,我又不能自己去選擇「臉」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:50.12,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,但是  埃米莉可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.58,0:19:54.13,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,埃米莉可努力去保護了自己珍視的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.34,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,你在成長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.26,0:20:05.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,是  我會變得更加能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:07.10,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,請您繼續教導我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:12.77,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,那下次要更愛惜你自己的身體了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.82,0:20:22.61,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,膝蓋擦破了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.87,0:20:27.49,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,為了快點痊癒就要早點休息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.71,0:20:36.59,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  完全睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.17,0:20:41.38,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明明睏了  但是在意的事情太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.76,0:20:45.09,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,明明活人偶不該想多餘的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.89,0:20:47.60,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:56.35,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,做個遺忘筆記本  把多餘的事情全部寫進去然後忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:58.48,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,首先在意的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.48,0:21:02.40,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,要怎樣做才更能幫到凱特小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.86,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,還有就是「露面」到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.91,0:21:11.08,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,之後是  偉大的祖父大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:15.62,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影宅是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.42,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這些東西我可不能說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.22,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:38.02,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,影宅  究竟是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.95,0:23:12.70,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,晚安  薩拉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.85,0:23:40.94,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,下集  黑灰導致的病
Comment: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.89,Shadow house-text,,0,0,0,,--ED--
